<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Dear Honeywell Customer,</span><br /><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"> Honeywell has signed an agreement on 23 April to sell our SECAN legal entity to an affiliate of Quantum Capital Partners AG. SECAN today consists of two sites: Gennevilliers and Vend&ocirc;me. This sale covers only the activities in Gennevilliers. The Vend&ocirc;me site will remain with Honeywell.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong><u>Vend&ocirc;me</u></strong></span><strong><br /> <br /> </strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Our site in Vendome will continue to remain with Honeywell and become a new legal entity &ndash; <strong>Honeywell Aerospace Vendome</strong> &ndash; on 26 June.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><u>How this change may impact you.&nbsp;&nbsp; </u></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span lang="EN-GB"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Your current Repair &amp; Overhaul orders will be automatically transferred from SECAN to Honeywell Aerospace Vend&ocirc;me as of 26 June.</span> <br /> <br /> </span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;" lang="EN-GB">For any Quality questions, please contact your Honeywell Quality Manager or Victor Perou at <a href="mailto:Victor.Perou@Honeywell.com">Victor.Perou@Honeywell.com</a>.</span><span lang="EN-GB"> <br /></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Following the 26 June Vend&ocirc;me transition, our Vend&ocirc;me financial accounting information will change. To avoid any disruption in service, please update your systems as needed. The new remittance banking account information is below.</span></li>
</ul>
