<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong><u>Gennevilliers</u></strong><u></u></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">We are pleased to say that we are on track to close the anticipated sale on 24 July 2015.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">After 24 July, all Air Management System product lines (including heat exchangers and vapor cycle air conditioning systems) design and manufacturing, and repair activities will continue to be performed by SECAN. Together, we are committed to ensuring a smooth transition for you, our customer, employees and suppliers. We have established a dedicated transition team to minimize any interruption in service.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">For any questions on Gennevilliers quality certification requirements ISO9001, AS9100, EASA PART21G, EASA PART145, NUCAP/PRI (special processes and NDT), or about the flow down of your Quality requirement, please contact Gilles Patry, Quality Leader, at +33140805985 or email <a href="mailto:Gilles.Patry@Honeywell.com">Gilles.Patry@Honeywell.com</a>.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">If you have any questions or concerns, please contact your Honeywell representative or send an email to </span><a href="http://goaero.honeywell.com/c000200Q0qZI04GXW00tN00"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">AeroCPSCommunications@Honeywell.com</span></a>.</p>
